posting_body: ['😁If you see this Ad then the Loft Home is Available😀', 'These amateur interior pictures taken after move out by home cleaner.', '620 Lowry Ave. N. 55411', 'Hello, I am Keith.', 'I am the building owner.', 'THIS Very Classic LOFT Home HAS GREAT PRIVACY.', 'This 1br Loft is Large and well updated with an "OPEN" FLOOR PLAN and High Ceilings', 'THIS Loft includes these rooms: 1 Bedroom + closet, Living Room, Dining Room, Kitchen w walk-in pantry, Bathroom.', 'The Bathroom has shower but no tub.', 'Ample On-street parking only.', 'This is a very well updated home yet classic details retained.', 'This 1br has Classic tall open archways instead of swinging doors this creates a flexible and grand living space here for a modern experience.', 'Hey, you may be able to bring Fido the dog or sneeky-pie the cat in on this home deal, too!!', '🐕🐈🦄🐫', 'Quiet Solo Office user downstairs.', 'Upstairs are only TWO LOFT HOMES/ FRONT AND REAR.', '1br Rear is available Right Now.', 'Please Tell me your name.', 'Add your contact phone number for an expedited response from me.', 'Tell me in general terms about you, your career, and your success.', 'What are your moving timeline goals?', 'From these lovely lofts you can Walk Or Bike to enjoy the Mississippi River, nearby.', 'You can cross the gorgeous LOWRY BRIDGE to FUN Northeast.', 'Great bus service to Downtown and the Warehouse District and Work.', 'Or just an easy bike ride to Downtown from here.', 'Here is a Terrific Live/Work Space to advance your professional career.', 'This is a nice deal for you to Enjoy!', 'Make this your home.', 'I pay water, sewer, rubbish.', 'Note:', '😀Lease period is ONE Full Year.', '😀']
